{"tid":2354051,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工等放工","createTime":"2021-01-05T07:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T11:22:23.000Z","uid":148260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dcc357124882ab970b2fd6cb632c69f098f3310c","tid":2354051,"uid":148260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"終於有工返 <br />\n<br />\n今日第二日返新工 帶我嗰個講到好想教我嘢但係佢又好忙 一啲嘢都冇俾過我做 雖然我唔忙係好事 但係全個office得我一個新仔 得我咁撚得閒<br />\n<br />\n我應該去問佢有冇咩俾我做定等佢得閒先俾嘢我做教我嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058f7b1f249a3ea885e5e3844458b43205de2c8e","tid":2354051,"uid":46459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"自己問下有咩文件可以睇住先"},{"pid":"6932c2445d0566cfdbac9bd48d6ced4317059bde","tid":2354051,"uid":279523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"享受下唔忙嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你學得越多野就會越忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 返左新工半年"},{"pid":"b1c2c7728470d60011c08cd824cdc5f2a3b88387","tid":2354051,"uid":92031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"冇野做咪搵同事吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}